data.name: lb_InfoForStep1.Text
data.value:
Position elbows to body at 90 degrees:
(1) Adjust height to the tips of your elbows.
(2) If feet don’t touch ground use a footrest lever to adjust height. Lever is under the seat.
(3) Lift lever and stand to raise the height.
(4) Lift lever and apply weight to lower the height
